This project is a chrome extension to aid the use of Wordreference API during browsing session.

Before packing this file creating the .crx extension, you should go to the API registration page and create your own API_key: http://www.wordreference.com/docs/APIregistration.aspx
then you have to substitute your key in
> src > js > api.js (line 8: PERSONAL_CODE)

You can find a detailed documentation about wr API here: http://www.wordreference.com/docs/api.aspx

WR API ToS: http://www.wordreference.com/docs/api.aspx
